name: We Need Space
description:
We need Space “anchored to the ground”.

PLTD Apung 1 is an electric generator ship in Banda Aceh, Sumatra, Indonesia that has become a tourist attraction. The 2,600-ton vessel had been in the sea. The tsunami flung it 2 to 3 kilometres inland by the 2004 Indian Ocean earthquake and tsunami.
